high_descs: Turn to the right and move forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Move to the counter at your left, with the plates on it.
Put the knife on the left most plate.
Pick up the left most plate on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink ahead of you.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the counter.
Turn left and face the counter on the right.
Put the knife on the white plate to the left on the counter.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the counter.
Turn around, head right towards the edge of the counter and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the plate with the knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife in a sink.

high_descs: Step to the right then move forward to the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife off of the counter.
Step to the left then turn and face the counter to the right.
Set the knife on the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate and knife off of the counter.
Turn around completely and move forward. Turn right and move forward to the sink
Place the knife and plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and knife to the sink.
